Nissin Men-nashi Donbei x Himote House: A collaboration between Himote House and Nissin. Each episode begins with an introduction by the talking cat Enishi and is followed by an ad-libbed performance by a member of the Himote House promoting Nissin's line of soup cups that substitute noodles with tofu.
['Nissin no Donbei x Kemono Friends', 'Himote House', 'Donbei x Kemurikusa']
